<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SDR | <%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #151515;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #000000;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            background-color: #f8a145;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .section:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .section li {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8a145;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000000;
        }
        .footer img {
            width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>About GPS-based Navigation Robot</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our about page! We are excited to introduce you to our GPS-based navigation robot.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Our robot utilizes GPS technology to navigate autonomously. It receives GPS coordinates and uses them to determine its current location and navigate to desired destinations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>GPS-based navigation</li>
            <li>Autonomous movement</li>
            <li>Real-time location tracking</li>
            <li>Customizable destination setting</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Applications</h2>
        <p>Our GPS-based navigation robot has various applications including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Delivery services</li>
            <li>Surveillance</li>
            <li>Mapping and exploration</li>
            <li>Search and rescue operations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
